PrecisVoiding of the election of STAN WALLACE, who was elected to the office of councillor by the MOUNT CURRIE BAND of Indians in British Columbia on January 27, 1991, due to a violation of the Indian Band Election Regulations which might have affected the results of the election.
Attachments
precis:
Voiding of the election of STAN WALLACE, who was elected to the office of
councillor by the MOUNT CURRIE BAND of Indians in British Columbia on
January 27, 1991, due to a violation of the Indian Band Election
Regulations which might have affected the results of the election.
